   1164           *   function details.
   1165           *   @li false - do not save and restore oscillators and clocks, see function
   1166           *   details.
   1167           * @par
   1168           *   The @p restore option should only be used if all clock control is done
   1169           *   via the CMU API.
   1170           ******************************************************************************/

